---

This software is a derivative work of the `mobile-env` project by Stefan Schneider (2021),
available at https://github.com/stefanbschneider/mobile-env.

Modifications were made by Elif Ohri (2025) as part of a PhD research project at Sorbonne University.  
These include substantial extensions for metaverse synchronization, Age of Information (AoI) metrics, 
multi-objective DRL optimization, and smart city simulation scenarios.
